---
import ToolLayout from '../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/lab-hud.css';
---

<ToolLayout
  title="轨道实验 · 从近地跳到更高轨道"
  description="看懂飞船怎么从低轨「搬家」到高轨：拖半径滑杆，看转移椭圆与两次点火耗油（霍曼转移示意）。"
  currentSlug="orbit-lab"
>
  <h1 slot="header">轨道实验</h1>
  <p class="intro">太空「搬家」：从近地圆轨道跳到更高圆轨道。拖滑杆改半径，看飞船沿椭圆飞过去，并读出两次点火耗多少油。</p>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Oxanium:wght@500;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />

  <div class="lab-hud">
    <p class="lab-story">
      <strong>这页干嘛：</strong>演示经典<strong>霍曼转移</strong>——先点火抬椭圆、飞半圈、再点火圆化。数字是相对单位（μ=1），用来比大小，不是真实 km/s。
    </p>

    <canvas id="orbit-canvas" class="lab-canvas-host" aria-label="霍曼转移示意"></canvas>

    <div class="lab-cards" aria-label="当前油耗">
      <div class="lab-card">
        <span class="lab-card-k">阶段</span>
        <span class="lab-card-v amber" id="orbit-phase">—</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lab-card">
        <span class="lab-card-k">第一次点火 Δv₁</span>
        <span class="lab-card-v" id="orbit-dv1">—</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lab-card">
        <span class="lab-card-k">油耗合计 Σ</span>
        <span class="lab-card-v amber" id="orbit-dvt">—</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lab-controls">
      <label>近地半径 r1 <span id="orbit-r1-val">1.00</span>
        <input type="range" id="orbit-r1" min="0.5" max="5" step="0.01" value="1" />
      </label>
      <label>目标半径 r2 <span id="orbit-r2-val">2.00</span>
        <input type="range" id="orbit-r2" min="0.5" max="7" step="0.01" value="2" />
      </label>
      <button type="button" class="lab-btn" id="orbit-play">暂停</button>
      <button type="button" class="lab-btn secondary" id="orbit-replay">重播</button>
      <button type="button" class="lab-btn secondary" id="orbit-preset-leo" data-r1="1" data-r2="1.5">低轨→稍高</button>
      <button type="button" class="lab-btn secondary" id="orbit-preset-geo" data-r1="1" data-r2="6.6">低轨→同步轨示意</button>
    </div>
    <p class="lab-meta">
      半长轴 a=<span class="lab-amber" id="orbit-a">—</span>
      · 第二次点火 Δv₂=<span id="orbit-dv2">—</span>
    </p>
    <p class="lab-note">仅演示共面双圆霍曼转移；「同步轨示意」只改半径比，不代表真实地球距离。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="lab-related">
    <h2>相关</h2>
    <a href="/space">轻星图</a>
    <a href="/tools/astro-today">今日星空</a>
    <a href="/tools/sat-pass">卫星过顶</a>
  </div>
</ToolLayout>

<style>
  #orbit-canvas {
    width: 100%;
    height: min(60vh, 520px);
  }
</style>

<script>
  import { bootOrbitLab } from '../../scripts/orbit-lab/main';
  bootOrbitLab();
</script>
